    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『星見フレンドフェス』当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "見て下さい！　さっき上げたこころとkanaさんの\nツーショット写真、すっごいバズってます！",
      "startTime": 5.9999997617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、凄く拡散されてるな。この後のこころ達の\nステージへの注目度も、間違いなく高まるだろう",
      "startTime": 13.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ふっ……その辺のシロウトさん達と\n計算し尽くされたこころ達の投稿は、全然違いますから",
      "startTime": 20.9986168703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか？　どこが違うのか、俺には分からないけど",
      "startTime": 26.024376472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "だから{user}さんはシロウトなんですよ\n顔の角度、光の加減、背景の映り込みチェック……",
      "startTime": 35.0986620427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "このパーフェクトな一枚を撮るために\nkanaさんとこころがどれだけ苦労したか……",
      "startTime": 42.631995376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かった分かった。SNSのバズりも計算通りなんだな\nそれなら、後は実際のパフォーマンス次第だ",
      "startTime": 50.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "心配ご無用です。リズノワともスリクスとも一味違った\nこころ達の新しい魅力に気付かせてあげますから",
      "startTime": 59.3357359728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "優勝はこころ達がいただきます。冠番組の企画も\n考えてあるんですよ？　例えばkanaさんへの～",
      "startTime": 67.4690693062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、それは優勝してからゆっくり聞くよ\nほら、もう時間だぞ",
      "startTime": 76.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、kanaちゃん、まだまだいくよ～！\nファンのみんなもしっかりついてきて下さいね？",
      "startTime": 84.5609947046,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6697.3819569000025,
          "startTime": 87.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "あっれ～？　おかしいですねぇ？\nぜんっぜん声が聞こえませんよ？",
      "startTime": 93.7943224431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "こころとkanaちゃんのファンは\nそんなに声が小さいんですかぁ？",
      "startTime": 99.4609936874,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4226.177946299998,
          "startTime": 101.394328038
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、立って、もっと声を出さないと\nこころ達に声が届きませんよ？　もーっと！",
      "startTime": 107.0943224431,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7551.851399300005,
          "startTime": 111.094328038
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "んー！　いい声出てますよー！\nよーし、それじゃあ、この調子でいきますよー！！",
      "startTime": 116.6609906357,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7251.267082799998,
          "startTime": 120.4610018254
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（ファンには受け入れられてるし、凄く盛り上がってる）\n（……二人の組み合わせが化学反応を起こしたのかもな）",
      "startTime": 127.8333404541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（リズノワともスリクスとも違って、バラバラな二人だ）\n（でもギャップが面白い……オンリーワンの魅力がある）",
      "startTime": 136.057639838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "みんな良く出来ました～。こころが褒めてあげます！\nご褒美の～、超絶悪魔的アイドルスマーイル！",
      "startTime": 145.7628619988,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10053.170776299992,
          "startTime": 151.1375886129
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10053.170776299992,
          "startTime": 151.1375886129
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "この前はお疲れ様、こころ。それと改めて――\n『ニコイチ仲良しユニット決定戦』、優勝おめでとう",
      "startTime": 161.0666737874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえそんな。褒められると困っちゃいます\n当然のことですから。でもありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 169.6669389247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "それに、不本意ではありましたけど、今回のユニットで\n『悪魔』っていうこころの新しい魅力が開花しましたし",
      "startTime": 178.7669389247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。いろいろ大変だったと思うけど\nこころにとっていい経験になったんじゃないか",
      "startTime": 186.9333404541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "はい。{user}さんにはとっても\nお世話になりました。勉強も見てもらいましたし",
      "startTime": 193.0991837977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんにも勉強を見てもらったって聞いたぞ\nなんだかんだ言って、仲良しじゃないか",
      "startTime": 200.9333404541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "はい。それに、二人が後押ししてくれたお陰で\n学校の居心地も、少しは良くなってきました",
      "startTime": 208.2692516802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……本当に、良かった\nでも全部こころの努力がもたらした結果だよ",
      "startTime": 215.8666737874,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10004.573233799987,
          "startTime": 225.8712470212
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないです。{user}さんには\nぜひお礼がしたくて………はいこれ、差し入れです",
      "startTime": 223.2379136878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_03-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "このプリン、人気過ぎて入手困難なんですよ？\nよ～く、味わって食べて下さいね？",
      "startTime": 232.8045874753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
